    {
      "id": "2077085874622464310",
      "text": "Introducing RockFocus - a focus timer for those who cultivate patiently, create continuously, and shape themselves over time.\n\nNotice what you keep returning to.\n\n1. Pick a label, so that you know what this session is for.\n2. Start the timer, stay focused to move the rock, like Sisyphus.\n3. When the session ends, you get a rock — and a clearer view of how your time adds up. See your focused sessions, minutes, streaks, heatmap, and where your passion actually goes.\n\nEvery effort counts, start seeing the shape of your time today.\n\nDownload Now👇👇\nhttps://t.co/j6mmIMy5Nl",
